          "section_content": [
            {
              "sentence": "During a gala organised by RadioMediaset\u00a0 [it] at Villa Nobel on 5 February on the occasion of the opening of the festival week, the local police received an anonymous call alerting about the presence of a bomb, and the venue was evacuated",
