              "refs": []
            },
            {
              "sentence": "The following day, a similar alert for the Teatro Ariston also proved to be unjustified and the caller was identified shortly after; he confessed to intentionally giving a false alarm\u00a0 [it] in order to disrupt the competition, and was scheduled for prosecution",
              "refs": [
                "https://www.escplus.es/eurovision/2024/la-television-ucraniana-va-a-emitir-el-benidorm-fest-2024-y-las-finales-nacionales-de-portugal-italia-estonia-letonia-lituania-alemania-y-finlandia/",
