              ]
            },
            {
              "sentence": "[e] Sergio was preemptively put under guard following threats",
              "refs": []
            },
            {
              "sentence": "Amadeus responded to Bar's comments by stating that \"any war in the world must be stopped\" and adding that the competing artists sent messages of \"peace, freedom of thought, racial equality, values\", in line with the \"inclusive\" spirit of the festival",
              "refs": [
                "https://www.rainews.it/tgr/bolzano/articoli/2024/02/manifestazione-filopalestinese-davanti-alla-sede-rai-di-bolzano--e229d83a-73c3-4147-bf4f-67798e3718a3.html"
